    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tikus Tales</strong> is a whimsical 3D platformer with a heavy focus on boss battles, starring two courageous mice, Suki and Tuki. When twelve rebellious animals stage a coup and imprison the Chinese Zodiac, only the mice manage to escape. Now, it's up to them to travel across a magical, Southeast Asia-inspired world - jumping, throwing, and battling their way through diverse environments - to restore balance to the Zodiac.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/8f476208e33aca3e5995f44093a8c11c.poster.avif?t=1771671321\" aria-label=\"Platforming action\" width=746 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/8f476208e33aca3e5995f44093a8c11c.webm?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/8f476208e33aca3e5995f44093a8c11c.mp4?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tikus Tales</strong><i> </i>blends stylized low-poly visuals with fast-paced, lighthearted combat and creative platforming sequences. Each boss battle is a multi-phase showdown - expect sudden twists like flooding arenas, chase sequences, and ever-changing rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/0e51a07f0a92375c228f881a6497706c.poster.avif?t=1771671321\" aria-label=\"One of the goofy bosses, Carmello the Camel\" width=746 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/0e51a07f0a92375c228f881a6497706c.webm?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/0e51a07f0a92375c228f881a6497706c.mp4?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With charm, humor, and a fresh twist on familiar legends, <i>Tikus Tales</i> offers a delightfully chaotic adventure full of surprises and personality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/f91b94bbe409d900dc025366347279af.poster.avif?t=1771671321\" aria-label=\"One of the imprisoned Zodiacs, the Ox.\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/f91b94bbe409d900dc025366347279af.webm?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/f91b94bbe409d900dc025366347279af.mp4?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/890ac5bb51041556ed11c4e0515b67f2.poster.avif?t=1771671321\" aria-label=\"Borrowing the power of the Ox to smash through stuff.\" width=746 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/890ac5bb51041556ed11c4e0515b67f2.webm?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1770880/extras/890ac5bb51041556ed11c4e0515b67f2.mp4?t=1771671321\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
